rows.label: xs04060100_SEL0011
rows.name: Step forward protectively in front of Lin.

rows.label: xs04060100_MSG0002
rows.name:
H-Hey, you're in the way!
I can't see![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04060100_MSG0003
rows.name:
Leave it to me!
I'll protect you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04060100_MSG0006
rows.name:
Ohh, to be grouped together with such barbarians...
How awful, just awful![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04060100_MSG0009
rows.name:
My individual designation is L'cirufe.
Please feel free to call me Lu.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04060100_MSG0010
rows.name:
Like the Nopon over there,
I am one who has lived on this planet since ancient times.[ST:wait ]
